== Theatre ==
Teatteri Kino Juha (Theatre Kino Juha) was established in Nurmijärvi, Finland 2009.
Kaikkien aikojen Pertsa ja Kilu in Taaborinvuori/ Nurmijärvi summer theatre 2009 & 2010. Script writer, director and actor. The cast included Laura Malmivaara, Maria Kuusiluoma, Sani Aartela, Anna Hanski, Eija Vilpas, Oskari Katajisto, Turkka Mastomäki and Ari-Kyösti Seppo.
Kaikkien aikojen Robin Hood in Taaborinvuori/ Nurmijärvi summer theatre 2011. Script writer, director and actor. The cast included Oskari Katajisto, Alina Tomnokiv, Eija Vilpas, Anna Hanski and Ari-Kyösti Seppo.
Gangsteri ja kaunotar in Taaborinvuori/ Nurmijärvi summer theatre 2012. Script writer, director. The cast included Eija Vilpas, Anna Hanski, Ari-Kyösti Seppo, Jussi Salminen.


